{"url": "https://pagesix.com/2017/10/24/carson-dalys-stepfather-dies-one-month-after-his-mom/", "text": "Carson Daly\u2018s stepfather, Richard Caruso, has passed away a little over a month after the death of Daly\u2019s mother.\n\n\u201cPops passed away today with absolute dignity & pride,\u201d the \u201cToday\u201d show host announced on social media Tuesday. \u201cThe greatest man we ever knew. Our hero. He exemplified great faith, loyalty to family & hard work. He provided us all with so much. We\u2019re grateful. His legacy lives on in all of us & anyone who had the pleasure of meeting him.\u201d\n\nHe continued, \u201cHe\u2019s reunited with mom now. Our faith remains strong. Thanks for your continued thoughts and prayers.\u201d\n\nEarlier on Tuesday, Daly explained to a fan asking why he\u2019s been absent from \u201cToday\u201d that he\u2019d had a \u201crough month\u201d and his dad\u2019s health was \u201cin peril.\u201d At the time, Daly planned to return to \u201cToday\u201d on Thursday, although it\u2019s not clear if that\u2019s changed since Caruso\u2019s passing.\n\nCaruso\u2019s cause of death is unknown.\n\nThe TV host\u2019s mom, Pattie Daly Caruso, died in September after suffering a sudden heart attack.\n\nHis rep did not immediately return our request for comment.", "images": ["https://pagesix.com/wp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F11%2F100-live-115674573.jpg?quality=75&strip=all&w=93&h=62&crop=1", "https://pagesix.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2017/10/gettyimages-104855671.jpg?quality=75&strip=all&w=1200", "https://pagesix.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/11/115743727.jpg?quality=75&strip=all&w=87", "https://pagesix.com/wp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2025%2F11%2F115485559.jpg?quality=75&strip=all&w=93&h=62&crop=1", "https://pagesix.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/11/kevin-spacey-reveals-homeless-living-115762000.jpg?quality=75&strip=all&w=260&h=174&crop=1", "https://pagesix.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/11/fergie.jpg?